nodes.text: The clan of Vylip F'alma was a Mustafarian cavern tribe on the planet Mustafar. The Priestess was also a member of the clan. The clan helped Corvax's descendant to kill the darkghast near the Corvax Fortress and participated in the battle against Fortress Vader.
Vylip F'alma's clan appears in Vader Immortal: A Star Wars VR Series, a three-part virtual reality series created by ILMxLAB.
